<item>
            <title>[LU-4234] Failure on test suite sanity-scrub test_4: fail to stop client</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4234</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/adbd0d60-47e6-11e3-a445-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/adbd0d60-47e6-11e3-a445-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_4 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fail to stop client!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;pdsh@client-26vm6: gethostbyname(&quot;client-26vm5&quot;) failed
 sanity-scrub test_4: @@@@@@ FAIL: Fail to stop client! 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>server and client: lustre-master build # 1751 RHEL6 ldiskfs</environment>
